1. Imam osetljivu *kožu*. (I have sensitive *skin*.)
2. Ovaj novčanik je napravljen od prave *kože*. (This wallet is made of genuine *leather*.)
3. Potrebno je da perete ruke sapunom i toplom vodom kako biste uklonili bakterije sa *kože*. (You need to wash your hands with soap and warm water to remove bacteria from your *skin*.)
4. On je imao težak pad i ogrebao je *kožu* na kolenima. (He had a hard fall and scraped his *skin* on his knees.)
5. Ova jakna ima mekanu *kožu*. (This jacket has a soft *leather*.)
6. Svake godine se menja *koža* na zmijama. (Every year, snakes shed their *skin*.)
7. Neki ljudi imaju alergiju na *kožu*. (Some people have an allergy to *skin*.)
8. Možete li mi preporučiti dobru hidratantnu kremu za *kožu* lica? (Can you recommend a good moisturizing cream for the *skin* on my face?)
9. Ovaj jastuk ima prevlaku od *kože* koja se može očistiti. (This pillow has a *leather* cover that can be cleaned.)
10. Ljudi su vekovima koristili *kožu* za izradu odeće i obuće. (People have been using *leather* to make clothing and footwear for centuries.)